	<p n="1">
		Prosperity! Fortune!		
	</p>
	
	<p n="15">
		24th year of the glorious king Rājentiracōḻa, the Lord, alias the king Irācakēcaripaṉmar,  
	</p>
	
	<p n="1-14">who ... [<foreign>meykkīrtti</foreign> of Rājendra I Cōḻa]</p>
	
	
	
	
